{"tid":967714,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺近年啲死仆街好鐘意喺巴士嘔 屌你老母","createTime":"2019-01-03T17:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T17:38:44.000Z","uid":11598,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"33343077e7a9aa5e12308da212ba19474753357a","tid":967714,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:12:48.000Z","msg":"你老味 九巴㗎新車本身已經膠味重 臭到仆街<br />\n有班撚屌成撚日係巴士上層尾到嘔<br />\n我屌你老母臭化，暈車浪就坐下層廢老座啦冚家鏟 走上去浪吓浪吓貪過癮咩<br />\n仲要唔知食撚咗乜柒 嘔出嚟臭過你老母個閪<br />\n車長好似又聞唔撚到咁唔port車照開<br />\n噏住成日臭撚到㗎車未埋站已經聞到啲酸縮屎味<br />\n<br />\n祝你班仆街急屎無廁紙 敏屎爛廁紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d069beecd79c968016583f14f92d781cce1be68f","tid":967714,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:14:35.000Z","msg":"好撚臭啊屌 suffer緊 仲有大半程車<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7904832312aedbfc86c09a29e2ca9b8b3c42d1","tid":967714,"uid":102132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:15:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fe6a1d60fda4ad4bc71bd317e7c9de2843581f0","tid":967714,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf7904832312aedbfc86c09a29e2ca9b8b3c42d1","tid":967714,"uid":102132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:15:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:16:17.000Z","msg":"you go"},{"pid":"ca56b8d5043a98db380dc9841c4f8eab6fe219b2","tid":967714,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:22:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42e352f118454dc888316e8a70fb5ae342df7f76","tid":967714,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:26:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bddd2e62da2b62c4968bd7bf7961b1b734f1af0","tid":967714,"uid":127870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"點分得出係因為暈車浪定食錯野定其他病而嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgm